%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrivate%20bus%20operators%20have%20gone%20on%20strike%20today%20in%20Haryana's%20Jind%20while%20those%20running%20autos%20too%20have%20opened%20a%20new%20front%20against%20the%20new%20law.%C2%A0The%20truckers%20allege%20the%20new%20law%20will%20discourage%20drivers%20from%20their%20duty%20and%20also%20prevent%20new%20ones%20to%20take%20up%20the%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20transporters%20say%20no%20one%20causes%20accidents%20intentionally%20and%20the%20drivers%20fear%20of%20being%20thrashed%20by%20a%20mob%20if%20they%20try%20to%20take%20the%20injured%20to%20hospital%2C%20demanding%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bblack%20law%26quot%3B%20be%20repealed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20expressed%20fear%20that%20if%20an%20accident%20happens%20due%20to%20the%20fog%2C%20the%20driver%20will%20be%20punished%20for%2010%20years%20without%20any%20fault%20of%20his.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETruckers%20had%20blocked%20NH-2%20in%20West%20Bengal's%20Hooghly%20district%20yesterday%20to%20protest%20the%20new%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDrivers%20fear%20being%20roughed%20up%20by%20locals%20after%20accidents%20and%20therefore%2C%20they%20try%20to%20flee%20such%20situations%20without%20reporting%20them%20to%20the%20authorities.%20Lengthy%20procedures%20involving%20the%20police%20are%20another%20reason%20that%20discourage%20them%20to%20take%20the%20legal%20route.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20(Second)%20Sanhita%2C%202023%20replaced%20the%20British-era%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20last%20year%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20simplify%20and%20Indianise%20the%20criminal%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704094320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fhq2thv7g_truckers-protest-pti_625x300_01_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftruckers-protest-new-law-that-increases-jail-term-for-road-accidents-4779682%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20change%20in%20the%20colonial-era%20criminal%20laws%20increasing%20jail%20t