0crime%2C%20along%20with%20other%20electronic%20evidence%2C%20have%20been%20seized%2C%20and%20the%20criminal%20history%20of%20the%20arrested%20individuals%20is%20currently%20under%20investigation%2C%20the%20TOI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fvaranasi%2Fbjp-it-cell-duo-among-3-held-for-iit-bhu-girls-gang-rape%2Farticleshow%2F106426429.cms%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20survivor%20had%20filed%20a%20complaint%20on%20November%202%2C%20prompting%20Lanka%20Police%20to%20register%20an%20FIR%20under%20sections%20354B%2C%20506%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(IPC)%2C%20and%2066E%20of%20the%20Information%20Technology%20(IT)%20Act.%20Subsequently%2C%20additional%20charges%20of%20gangrape%20(Section%20376%20D)%20and%20outraging%20a%20woman%E2%80%99s%20modesty%20(Section%20509)%20were%20added%20after%20the%20student%E2%80%99s%20statement%20was%20recorded%20before%20a%20magistrate%20on%20November%208.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20survivor%E2%80%99s%20account%2C%20she%20was%20on%20a%20walk%20outside%20her%20hostel%20with%20a%20friend%20from%20the%20same%20institute%20on%20November%201.%20They%20were%20confronted%20by%20the%20accused%2C%20who%20were%20on%20a%20motorbike%2C%20near%20the%20Karmanbir%20Baba%20temple%20on%20campus.%20The%20survivor%20was%20forcibly%20separated%20from%20her%20friend%2C%20dragged%20behind%20some%20bushes%2C%20and%20assaulted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20sparked%20massive%20protests%20on%20campus%20with%20thousands%20of%20students%20demonstrating%20for%20better%20security%20measures%20and%20swift%20police%20action%20in%20the%20case.%20The%20delay%20in%20arresting%20the%20accused%20prompted%20further%20demonstrations%20near%20the%20office%20of%20the%20institute%E2%80%99s%20director.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20scuffle%20had%20also%20broken%20out%20between%20members%20of%20the%20Akhil%20Bharatiya%20Vidya%20Parishad%20(ABVP)%2C%20All%20India%20Students%20Association