At%20Unravelling%20Universe's%20Big%20Mystery%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAt%209.32%20am%2C%20ISRO%20announced%20that%20the%20lift-off%20of%20the%20Polar%20Satellite%20Launch%20Vehicle%20(PSLV)%20was%20normal%20and%20XPoSAT%20was%20launched%20successfully.%20%26quot%3BPSLV-C58%20vehicle%20placed%20the%20satellite%20precisely%20into%20the%20intended%20orbit%20of%20650%20km%20with%206-degree%20inclination.%20The%20POEM-3%20is%20being%20scripted%2C%26quot%3B%20ISRO%20posted%20in%20X.%20Soon%20after%2C%20ISRO%20chief%20S%20Somanath%20announced%20the%20successful%20launch.%20POEM%20refers%20to%C2%A0PSLV%20Orbital%20Experimental%20Module.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAstrophysicist%20Dipankar%20Bhattacharya%20told%20NDTV%20that%20today's%20launch%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Btextbook%20launch%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThe%20expected%20orbit%20has%20been%20achieved.%20Now%20all%20the%20expected%20science%20is%20hopefully%20going%20to%20work%20as%20planned%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20XPoSAT%20mission%20launch%20also%20marked%20the%2060th%20flight%20of%20the%20Polar%20Satellite%20Launch%20Vehicle%20(PSLV).%20The%20260-tonne%20rocket%20carries%20an%20advanced%20astronomy%20observatory%20meant%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fisro-mission-launch-to-study-black-holes-and-neutron-stars-successful-says-isro-chief-s-somanath-4778995%5C%22%3Eto%20study%20black%20holes%20and%20neutron%20stars%3C%2Fa%3E.%20With%20this%2C%20India%20has%20become%20the%20second%20country%20after%20the%20US%20to%20have%20such%20a%20specialised%20'observatory'%20of%20this%20kind%20to%20study%20black%20holes.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EUsing%20X-ray%20photons%20and%20their%20polarisation%2C%20XPoSAT%20will%20help%20study%20the%20radiation%20from%20near%20black%20holes%20and%20neutron%20stars.%20It%20carries%20two%20payloads%20--%20POLIX%20(Polarimeter%20Instrument%20in%20X-rays)%20and%20XSPECT%20(X-ray%20Spectroscopy%20and%20Timing).%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20satellite%20will%20measure%20polarisation%20of%20X-rays%20in%20the%20energy%20band%208-30keV%20emanating%20from%20about%2050%20potential%20cosmic%20sources%20through%20Thomson%20Scattering%20by%20POLIX%20payload.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIt%20will%20carry%20out%20long%20term%20spectral%20and%20temporal%20studies%20of%20cosmic%20X-ray%20sources.%20It%20will%20also%20carry%20out%20polarisation%20and%20spectroscopic%20measurements%20of%20X-ray%20emissions%20from%20cosmic%20sources%20through%20POLIX%20and%20XSPECT%20payloads.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhen%20stars%20run%20out%20of%20fuel%20and%20'die'%2C%20they%20collapse%20under%20their%20own%20gravity%20and%20leave%20behind%20black%20holes%20or%20neutron%20stars.%20Black%20holes%20have%20the%20highest%20gravitational%20force%20in%20the%20universe%2C%20and%20neutron%20stars%20have%20the%20highest%20densities.%C2%A0Gathering%20more%20information%20on%20this%2C%20the%20mission%20will%20help%20unravel%20mysteries%20of%20ultra-extreme%20environments%20in%20space.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20XPoSat%20satellite%20cost%20around%20Rs%20250%20crore%20(approximately%20%2430%20million).%20The%20NASA%20IXPE%20--%20which%20is%20on%20a%20similar%20mission%20since%202021%20--%20cost%20%24188%20million.%20The%20Indian%20satellite%20is%20expected%20to%20last%20more%20than%20five%20years%2C%20compared%20to%20the%20two-year%20life%20span%20of%20the%20NASA%20IXPE.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFormer%20ISRO%20chairman%20G%20Madhavan%20Nair%20has%20said%20the%20PSLV%20rocket%20system%20has%20evolved%20as%20the%20most%20reliable%20and%20cost-effective%20one%20in%20the%20global%20scenario.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20look%20back%20in%20history%2C%20we%20started%20this%20journey%20in%201993%20and%20since%20then%2C%20most%20of%20the%20missions%20have%20been%20successfully%20completed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E2023%20was%20a%20great%20year%20for%20ISRO%20and%20the%20country.%20The%20success%20of%20the%20Chandrayaan%20mission%20put%20India%20into%20the%20elite%20space%20club%2C%20with%20the%20distinction%20of%20being%20the%20only%20country%20to%20achieve%20a%20soft%20landing%20near%20the%20South%20Pole%20of%20the%20moon.%20As%202024%20begins%2C%20ISRO%20has%20its%20eyes%20focused%20on%20the%20Gaganyaan%20launch%2C%20India's%20first%20human%20spaceflight%20programme.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704093780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fp70abqc_isro-launch-new_625x300_01_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fxposat-launch-isro-launches-mission-to-study-black-holes-2nd-after-nasa-to-do-so-4778881%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20New%20Year's%20Day%2C%20India%20started%20a%20new%20mission%20to%20solve%20what%20is%20among%20the%20oldest%20mysteries%20of%20the%20universe%20-%20black%20holes.%20At%209.10%20am%2C%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%20launched%20the%20XPoSAT%20or%20X-ray%20Polarimeter%20Sat%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fxposat-launch-isro-launches-mission-to-study-black-holes-2nd-after-nasa-to-do-so-4778881%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fxposat-launch-isro-launches-mission-to-study-black-holes-2nd-after-nasa-to-do-so-4778881%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fxposat-launch-isro-launches-mission-to-study-black-holes-2nd-after-nasa-to-do-so-4778881%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dunki%20giving%20tough%20competition%20to%20Salaar%20in%20USA%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704093608000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106442647%2Cimgsize-52354.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fbox-office%2Fdunki-giving-tough-competition-to-s