2C%20and%20many%20other%20leaders%20issued%20statements%20about%20her%20death%20after%20her%20son%20posted%20about%20it%20on%20Facebook.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dallasnews.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2F2023%2F12%2F31%2Feddie-bernice-johnson-88-broke-barriers-left-huge-mark-on-dallas-in-long-house-career%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EThe%20Dallas%20Morning%20News%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20confirmed%20her%20death%20with%20an%20unnamed%20source%20close%20to%20the%20family.%20No%20cause%20of%20death%20was%20given.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBiden%20hailed%20her%20%26quot%3Bimmense%20courage%26quot%3B%20and%20called%20her%20%26quot%3Ban%20icon%20and%20mentor%20to%20generations%20of%20public%20servants%2C%20through%20whom%20her%20legacy%20of%20resilience%20and%20purpose%20will%20endure.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20was%20the%20single%20most%20effective%20legislator%20Dallas%20has%20ever%20had%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20mayor%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BNobody%20brought%20more%20federal%20infrastructure%20money%20home%20to%20our%20city.%20Nobody%20fought%20harder%20for%20our%20communities%20and%20our%20residents'%20interests%20and%20safety.%20And%20nobody%20knew%20how%20to%20navigate%20Washington%20better%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Dallas.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkamala-harris-franklin-foer-book-the-last-politician-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20praised%20the%20late%20politician%2C%20calling%20Johnson%20a%20%26quot%3Bpioneer%26quot%3B%20and%20recalled%20her%20time%20working%20alongside%20Johnson%20in%20the%20Congressional%20Black%20Caucus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20a%20young%20age%2C%20she%20witnessed%20and%20experienced%20the%20profound%20effects%20of%20segregation%20and%20decided%20she%20would%20not%20stay%20on%20the%20sidelines%20in%20the%20fight%20for%20justice%2C%26quot%3B%20Harris%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohnson%20served%20in%20the%20House%20for%20three%20decades%20after%20becoming%20the%20first%20registered%20nurse%20elected%20to%20Congress%20and%20the%20first%20Black%20chief%20psychiatric%20nurse%20at%20Dallas'%20Veterans%20Affairs%20hospital.%20She%20went%20on%20to%20become%20the%20first%20Black%20woman%20to%20chair%20the%20House%20Committee%20on%20Science%2C%20Space%2C%20and%20Technology%20and%20also%20led%20the%20Congressional%20Black%20Caucus.%20She%20left%20office%20in%20January%20after%20repeatedly%20delaying%20her%20retirement.%20Before%20Congress%2C%20she%20served%20in%20the%20Texas%20legislature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohnson%20announced%20her%20retirement%20in%202021%20and%20later%20tapped%20Texas%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhich-members-congress-student-loan-payments-resume-october-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERep.%20Jasmine%20Crockett%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20run%20as%20her%20replacement.%20Crockett%20is%20currently%20serving%20in%20the%20same%20seat%20that%20Johnson%20left.%20In%20a%20statement%20following%20Johnson's%20death%2C%20Crockett%20recalled%20getting%20the%20call%20from%20Johnson%20asking%20her%20to%20take%20over%20her%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20I%20was%20honored%2C%20I%20was%20also%20bewildered%20when%20Chairwoman%20Johnson%20called%20me%20and%20asked%20me%20to%20run%20to%20represent%20Texas%2030%2C%26quot%3B%20Crockett%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20only%20a%20freshman%20in%20the%20Texas%20House%2C%20and%20never%20in%20my%20wildest%20dreams%20would%20I%20think%20that%20she%20was%20aware%20of%20anything%20that%20I%20was%20doing%20in%20the%20House.%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECrockett%2C%20however%2C%20praised%20Johnson's%20intuition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20that%20is%20the%20thing%20about%20her%3A%20she%20never%20slept.%20She%20was%20always%20working%2C%26quot%3B%20Crockett%20said.%20%26quot%3BShe%20kept%20her%20finger%20on%20the%20pulse%20of%20what%20was%20going%20on%20in%20the%20Texas%20House%2C%20and%20while%20I%20didn't%20fully%20understand%20what%20I%20was%20getting%20myself%20into%2C%20I%20trusted%20her%2C%20her%20judgment%2C%20and%20her%20mentorship.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohnson%20used%20her%20committee%20leadership%20position%20to%20fight%20against%20Republican%20efforts%20to%20block%20action%20on%20climate%20change.%20Congressional%20Black%20Caucus%20Chair%20Steven%20Horsford%20said%20Johnson%20was%20also%20%26quot%3Ba%20fierce%20advocate%20for%20expanding%20STEM%20opportunities%20to%20Black%20and%20minority%20students%26quot%3B%20who%20also%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20helping%20the%20Biden%20administration%20pass%20a%20major%20package%20of%20incentives%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-building-factories-census-data-chips-act-inflation-reduction-act-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecomputer%20chip%20manufacturers%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20born%20in%20Waco%20and%20grew%20up%20in%20the%20segregated%20South.%20Dallas'%20once-segregated%20Union%20Station%20was%20renamed%20in%20her%20honor%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20own%20experience%20with%20racism%20helped%20spur%20her%20to%20get%20involved%20in%20politics.%20She%20recalled%20that%20officials%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhomelessness-us-veterans-increase-largest-margin-yet-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVA%20hospital%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20shocked%20that%20she%20was%20Black%20after%20they%20hired%20her%20sight-unseen%2C%20so%20they%20rescinded%20their%20offer%20for%20her%20to%20live%20in%20a%20dorm%20on%20campus.%20She%20told%20The%20Dallas%20Morning%20News%20in%202020%20that%20officials%20would%20go%20into%20patients'%20rooms%20ahead%20of%20her%20to%20%26quot%3Bsay%20that%20I%20was%20qualified.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20was%20really%20the%20most%20blatant%2C%20overt%20racism%20that%20I%20ever%20experienced%20in%20my%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohnson%20nearly%20quit%20but%20decided%20to%20stick%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20very%20challenging%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20any%20job%20where%20you're%20an%20African%20American%20woman%20entering%20for%20the%20first%20time%20would%20be%20a%20challenge.%20They%20had%20not%20hired%20one%20before%20I%20got%20there.%20Yes%2C%20it%20was%20a%20challenge%2C%20but%20it%20was%20a%20successful%20venture.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftexas-us-rep-eddie-bernice-johnson-dead-at-88-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704082714000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65923cfaab6f2ebb11f7fe06%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftexas-us-rep-eddie-bernice-johnson-dead-at-88-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Trailblazing%20US%20Rep.%20Eddie%20Bernice%20Johnson%2C%20a%20nurse%20from%20Texas%20who%20helped%20bring%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20federal%20dollars%20to%20the%20Dallas%20area%2C%20has%20died.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22hgetahun%40insider.com%20(Hannah%20Getahun%2CAssociated%20Press)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A19%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftexas-us-rep-eddie-bernice-johnson-dead-at-88-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jeremy%20Renner%20Set%20to%20Head%20Back%20to%20Work%20on%20%E2%80%98Mayor%20of%20Kingstown%E2%80%99%20a%20Year%20After%20Near-Fatal%20Snowplow%20Accident%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704082692000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2FGettyImages-1354989348-1.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235840345%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jeremy%20Renner%20has%20r