icult%20to%20resist%20the%20feeling%20that%20had%20the%20video%20of%20torture%20not%20come%20out%20in%20the%20public%20domain%2C%20the%20three%20dead%20men%20would%20have%20ended%20up%20being%20statistics%2C%20adding%20to%20the%20number%20of%20disappeared%20persons%20in%20Kashmir%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20insurgency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20this%20background%2C%20the%20twin%20emotions%20that%20I%20felt%20upon%20learning%20about%20the%20incident%20was%20d%C3%A9j%C3%A0%20vu.%20And%20sadness.%20Not%20for%20the%20unfortunate%20Kashmiris.%20But%20for%20the%20institution%20called%20the%20Indian%20Army%2C%20which%20has%20progressively%20and%20steadily%20been%20losing%20its%20moral%20bearings%20in%20the%20quicksand%20of%20counter-insurgency%20operations.%20On%20this%20climb%20down%20the%20ladder%20of%20military%20professionalism%2C%20the%20Indian%20Army%20faced%20several%20stages%20from%20which%20it%20could%20have%20turned%20back%20%E2%80%93%20back%20to%20its%20core%20values%20%E2%80%93%20but%20it%20chose%20to%20continue%20trudging%20downwards.%20Hell%20does%20sucks%20you%20in%20with%20all%20kinds%20of%20allurements%20%E2%80%93%20recognition%2C%20gallantry%20awards%2C%20headiness%20of%20power%2C%20glamour%20of%20media%20attention%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailyexcelsior.com%2Fofficers-among-23-army-men-who-face-cbi-case-for-alleged-corruption%2F%5C%22%3Eavenues%20of%20money%20making%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETruth%20be%20told%2C%20there%20has%20been%20an%20inevitability%20to%20this.%20The%20Indian%20Army%20is%20the%20only%20military%20force%20in%20the%20world%20to%20combat%20insurgency%20within%20its%20own%20territory%20%E2%80%93%20for%20over%2070%20years%20in%20the%20Northeast%20and%2030%20years%20in%20Kashmir.%20It%20would%20have%20been%20a%20miracle%20if%20it%20remained%20unaffected%20by%20the%20vested%20interests%20that%20develop%20when%20political%20problems%20remain%20unresolved%20for%20an%20extended%20period%20of%20time.%20Moreover%2C%20continuous%20exposure%20to%20debilitating%20violence%2C%20both%20inflicted%20upon%20you%20and%20inflicted%20by%20you%2C%20brutalises%20the%20victim%20and%20the%20perpetrator%20alike%2C%20so%20much%20so%20that%20after%20a%20point%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20distinguish%20who%E2%80%99s%20who.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20stages%20in%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20descent%20into%20unprofessionalism%20were%20dehumanisation%20of%20the%20adversary%2C%20whataboutery%20on%20human%20rights%20issues%2C%20communalisation%20of%20the%20threats%20and%20political%20alignment%20for%20personal%20aggrandisement.%20Unless%20we%20understand%20this%20downward%20trajectory%2C%20we%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20able%20to%20put%20the%20present%20incident%20in%20its%20correct%20context.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20early%20years%20of%20my%20reporting%20on%20the%20Indian%20Army%E2%80%99s%20counter-insurgency%20operations%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20I%20came%20across%20the%20story%20of%20Kunan-Poshpora.%20This%20was%20in%202005.%20Like%20most%20newcomers%20on%20the%20%E2%80%98army%20beat%E2%80%99%2C%20I%20was%20full%20of%20nationalistic%20fervour%2C%20so%20my%20instinctive%20reaction%20was%20disbelief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRaping%20women%20is%20not%20one%20of%20Indian%20Army%E2%80%99s%20KRAs%20(key%20result%20areas)%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20very%20senior%20Srinagar-based%20officer%20had%20told%20me%20tersely%20in%202003%20during%20my%20first%20assignment.%20We%20were%20talking%20about%20the%20possible%20human%20rights%20violations%20by%20the%20Indian%20Army%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20and%20he%20had%20taken%20umbrage%20at%20my%20artless%20question.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20get%20up%20in%20morning%20and%20brief%20our%20men%20that%20they%20have%20to%20rape%20two%20women%20and%20kill%20four%20men%20today%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20in%20a%20tone%20that%20shut%20me%20up%20right%20and%20proper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHence%2C%20when%20one%20Kashmiri%20journalist%20mentioned%20the%20Kunan-Poshpora%20incident%20to%20me%2C%20I%20dismissed%20it%20as%20separatists%E2%80%99%20propaganda%20to%20malign%20the%20Indian%20Army.%20For%20the%20uninitiated%2C%20Kunan-Poshpora%20is%20a%20village%20in%20the%20Kupwara%20district%20of%20north%20Kashmir.%20And%20the%20%E2%80%98incident%E2%80%99%20refers%20to%20the%20horrific%20night%20of%20February%2023%2C%201991%2C%20when%20in%20the%20course%20of%20a%20cordon%20and%20search%20operation%20by%20an%20Indian%20Army%20unit%2C%20almost%20two%20dozen%20women%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thepolisproject.com%2Fread%2Fit-was-not-rape-it-was-war-that-night-in-kunan-poshpora%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%20being%20gangraped%3C%2Fa%3E.%20There%20were%20several%20enquiries%2C%20but%20the%20findings%20remained%20polarised.%20The%20villagers%20and%20the%20women%20stood%20by%20their%20version%20and%20the%20army%20by%20its%20denial.%20No%20one%20was%20ever%20prosecuted.%20Even%20today%2C%20the%20incident%20remains%20between%20the%20grey%20intersection%20of%20facts%20and%20fiction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22J%26amp%3BK%3A%20Families%20Affected%20by%20'Fake%20Encounters'%20View%20Poonch%20Civilian%20Deaths%20with%20Doubts%20and%20Despair%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fjk-families-affected-by-fake-encounters-view-poonch-civilian-deaths-with-doubts-and-despair%5C%22%3EJ%26amp%3BK%3A%20Families%20Affected%20by%20%E2%80%98Fake%20Encounters%E2%80%99%20View%20Poonch%20Civilian%20Deaths%20with%20Doubts%20and%20Despair%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20was%20my%20confidence%20in%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20Indian%20Army%2C%20that%20my%20disbelief%20was%20not%20enough.%20I%20needed%20validation%20too.%20Especially%2C%20when%20I%20learnt%20about%20Kunan-Poshpora%20months%20after%20the%20Manorama%20Devi%20incident%20of%20Manipur.%20Manorama%20Devi%20was%20picked%20up%20from%20her%20home%20by%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%20for%20questioning%20in%20July%202004.%20Later%20her%20bullet-ridden%20body%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hrw.org%2Freports%2F2008%2Findia0908%2F3.htm%5C%22%3Ewas%20found%20in%20a%20field%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20gunshots%20to%20her%20genitals%2C%20apparently%20to%20remove%20evidence%20of%20rape.%20Thereafter%2C%20Manipuri%20women%20came%20out%20to%20protest%20against%20the%20impunity%20with%20which%20they%20thought%20the%20Indian%20Army%20operated%20in%20the%20state.%20Assam%20Rifles%20is%20officered%20by%20the%20army.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fif-you-remember-manipuri-women-only-for-nude-protest-against-army-think-again-1436411-2019-01-22%5C%22%3Eimage%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20naked%20protest%20by%20women%20holding%20the%20banner%20%E2%80%98Indian%20Army%20Rape%20Us%E2%80%99%20refused%20to%20leave%20my%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDisturbed%20by%20this%20consecutive%20shaking-up%20of%20my%20beliefs%2C%20I%20sought%20an%20appointment%20with%20the%20seniormost%20officer%20in%20Delhi%20responsible%20for%20public%20information.%20The%20two-star%20general%20graciously%20received%20me%20in%20his%20office%2C%20gave%20me%20tea%20and%20biscuits%2C%20before%20proceeding%20to%20put%20my%20concerns%20to%20rest.%20By%20way%20of%20breaking%20the%20ice%2C%20he%20asked%20me%20about%20my%20family%20background%2C%20my%20career%20goals%20and%20so%20on.%20Finally%2C%20he%20got%20down%20to%20the%20main%20issue.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20like%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9Chave%20different%20moral%20values.%20Can%20you%20come%20out%20on%20the%20streets%20naked%20to%20protest%2C%20whatever%20be%20the%20provocation%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked%20rhetorically.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20like%20us%20will%20not%20do%20that.%20Their%20society%20is%20different%20from%20ours.%20Their%20attitude%20towards%20sex%20is%20different.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20tackled%20Manipur%2C%20he%20proceeded%20to%20Kashmir.%20%E2%80%9CKashmir%20looks%20like%20a%20conservative%20society%2C%20but%20they%20are%20extremely%20fanatic%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CKashmiri%20women%20take%20great%20pride%20in%20having%20sex%20with%20the%20Jihadis.%20They%20regard%20it%20as%20their%20contribution%20to%20Jihad.%20They%20have%20no%20shame%20in%20saying%20that%20they%20have%20been%20raped%20to%20malign%20the%20Indian%20Army.%20That%E2%80%99s%20part%20of%20their%20psychological%20warfare.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20me%20a%20long%20time%20to%20process%20this%20conversation.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20correct%20vocabulary%20to%20understand%20that%20dehumanisation%20of%20the%20adversary%2C%20whether%20in%20Kashmir%20or%20the%20Northeast%2C%20was%20one%20of%20the%20means%20of%20getting%20the%20soldiers%20to%20carry%20out%20unsoldierly%20and%20unprofessional%20acts.%20This%20dehumanisation%20was%20necessary%20to%20absolve%20oneself%20of%20the%20guilt%20of%20treating%20a%20fellow%20being%20as%20less%20than%20human.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20don%E2%80%99t%20feel%20any%20compunctions%20in%20pulling%20out%20an%20elderly%20man%20from%20his%20vehicle%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20his%20family%20and%20humiliating%20him%2C%20because%20%E2%80%98Kashmiris%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20same%20sense%20of%20dignity%20that%20we%20have.%E2%80%99%20You%20don%E2%80%99t%20flinch%20when%20you%20torture%20a%20young%20boy%20because%20%E2%80%98They%20are%20used%20to%20much%20worse%20hardships.%E2%80%99%20You%20are%20not%20horrified%20when%20you%20%E2%80%98accidentally%E2%80%99%20kill%20an%20innocent%20person%20because%20%E2%80%98if%20they%20really%20cared%20about%20life%20would%20they%20let%20their%20children%20join%20the%20militancy.%E2%80%99%20And%20so%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20dehumanisation%20can%20only%20go%20this%20far.%20Sometimes%2C%20the%20human%20rights%20types%20ask%20too%20many%20pesky%20questions%2C%20which%20require%20a%20response.%20So%2C%20throw%20the%20question%20back.%20Much%20before%20whataboutery%20became%20the%20nationalist%E2%80%99s%20reflex%20on%20the%20social%20media%2C%20the%20Indian%20Army%20officers%20had%20perfected%20it%20in%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20seminar%20on%20human%20rights%20that%20the%20army%20had%20organised%20in%20a%20Rashtriya%20Rifle%20unit%20in%20Pattan%20in%20the%20early%20years%20of%20the%20last%20decade%2C%20I%20was%20invited%20as%20a%20speaker.%20A%20senior%20officer%20who%20spoke%20after%20me%2C%20politely%20rebuked%20my%20talk%20by%20saying%20%E2%80%98What%20about%20the%20human%20rights%20of%20the%20soldiers%3F%E2%80%99%20That%20set%20the%20tone%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20his%20talk.%20He%20gave%20examples%20of%20the%20brutality%20of%20the%20militants%20and%20the%20plight%20of%20the%20families%20of%20the%20killed%20army%20personnel.%20He%20spoke%20about%20watching%20his%20brother%20in%20arms%20bleed%20to%20death%20in%20front%20of%20him%2C%20or%20his%20buddy%20losing%20a%20limb.%20Sure%20enough%2C%20it%20was%20a%20whistle-worthy%20speech.%20The%20officer%20got%20a%20standing%20ovation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20during%20tea%2C%20I%20was%20accosted%20by%20many%20young%20officers%20who%20repeated%20the%20rhetoric%20of%20their%20senior%2C%20with%20additional%20examples.%20My%20assertion%20that%20soldiers%20and%20insurgents%20are%20held%20to%20different%20moral%20and%20professional%20standards%20went%20unheard%20and%20unheeded.%20Clearly%2C%20there%20can%20be%20no%20persuasive%20answer%20to%20the%20question%20that%20begins%20with%20%E2%80%98what%20about.%E2%80%99%20In%20any%20case%2C%20the%20person%20asking%20the%20question%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20want%20the%20answer.%20The%20righteousness%20of%20their%20question%20is%20the%20answer%20in%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20biggest%20erosion%20has%20been%20of%20Indian%20Army%E2%80%99s%20secular%20values%2C%20which%20now%20also%20shape%20its%20attitude%20towards%20CI%20Ops%20in%20Kashmir.%20Many%20retired%20military%20officers%20rue%20the%20growing%20politicisation%20of%20the%20Indian%20Army.%20But%20the%20politicisation%20has%20only%20been%20possible%20because%20there%20was%20communalisation%20of%20the%20army%20first.%20Senior%20officers%2C%20especially%20from%20the%20retired%20community%2C%20are%20fond%20of%20throwing%20the%20examples%20of%20common%20prayer%20rooms%20in%20an%20army%20unit%2C%20called%20%3Cem%3ESarva%20Dharm%20Sthal%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20of%20unit%20officers%20practicing%20the%20religious%20rituals%20of%20their%20troops%20irrespective%20of%20their%20personal%20beliefs%20to%20underscore%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20syncretism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20truth%20is%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20mere%20tokenism.%20And%20all%20officers%20know%20that.%20As%20everything%20else%20in%20the%20army%2C%20religious%20syncretism%20is%20also%20a%20parade.%20And%20it%20has%20a%20cute%20name%20too.%20It%E2%80%99s%20called%20mandir%20parade.%20Syncretism%20or%20tolerance%20is%20not%20what%20you%20display.%20It%20is%20what%20you%20believe.%20And%20believe%20so%20deeply%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20like%20breathing%20to%20you.%20Religious%20tolerance%20by%20order%20is%20no%20tolerance%3B%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20timebound%20duty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20communalisation%20of%20the%20Indian%20Army%20is%20not%20its%20fault.%20With%20the%20Islamic%20Republic%20of%20Pakistan%20as%20the%20primary%20military%20threat%2C%20religion%20was%20always%20a%20factor%20in%20its%20mental%20preparedness%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20infantry%2C%20where%20pure%20units%20had%20religious%20war%20cries.%20Once%20the%20insurgency%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20increasingly%20assumed%20an%20Islamist%20character%20through%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20interventions%2C%20the%20internal%20enemy%20also%20increasingly%20started%20looking%20and%20behaving%20like%20a%20Muslim.%20If%20the%20army%20was%20not%20involved%20in%20CI%20Ops%20for%20a%20prolonged%20period%2C%20it%20would%20have%20been%20in%20the%20cantonment%20or%20training%20institutes%20preparing%20and%20training%20for%20conventional%20warfare.%20The%20impressionable%20soldiers%20and%20young%20officers%20would%20have%20been%20removed%20from%20the%20society%20where%20religious%20polarisation%20was%20becoming%20an%20everyday%20reality.%20And%20they%20may%20have%20taken%20mandir%20parade%20as%20the%20way%20of%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20did%20not%20happen.%20The%20army%20was%20forced%20to%20train%20primarily%20for%20counter%20terrorism%2C%20especially%20after%20the%20Modi%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pmindia.gov.in%2Fen%2Fnews_updates%2Fpms-address-at-the-combined-commanders-conference%2F%5C%22%3Edeemed%20terrorism%20as%20India%E2%80%99s%20main%20threat%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Moreover%2C%20to%20isolate%20the%20Kashmir%20issue%20from%20its%20political%20context%2C%20the%20term%20insurgency%20was%20replaced%20by%20terrorism%20by%20the%20government.%20So%20effectively%2C%20the%20army%20was%20now%20training%20to%20fight%20Muslim%20and%20Christian%20terrorists.%20Consequently%2C%20it%20saw%20nothing%20wrong%20in%20issuing%20a%20tender%20for%20creating%20a%20simulated%20village%20in%20Officers%E2%80%99%20Training%20Academy%2C%20Gaya%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fforceindia.net%2Ffirstperson%2Fprejudice-train%2F%5C%22%3Ein%20which%20it%20asked%20for%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%9Camong%20other%20things%2C%20structures%20of%20village%20huts%20with%20different%20specifications%20of%20material%20and%20sizes%2C%20a%20mosque%20and%20a%20church.%E2%80%99%20It%20also%20asked%20for%20%E2%80%98mannequins%20to%20be%20dressed%20in%20%3Cem%3Epherans%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Eburkhas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Epathani%3C%2Fem%3E%20suits%2C%20skull%20caps%2C%20traditional%20clothing%20of%20women%20from%20the%20Northeast%20and%20robes%20of%20a%20Christian%20priest.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProlonged%20deployment%20of%20the%20army%20in%20CI%20Ops%20in%20Kashmir%20and%20the%20Northeast%20gradually%20turned%20it%20into%20a%20mostly%20Hindu%20army%2C%20with%20Hinduism%20being%20conflated%20with%20nationalism.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tbsnews.net%2Fworld%2Fsouth-asia%2Fhinduism-way-life-not-religion-indian-supreme-court-592694%5C%22%3EWhen%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20also%20says%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Hinduism%20is%20a%20way%20of%20life%20and%20not%20a%20religion%2C%20how%20can%20one%20blame%20a%20mere%20military%20service%20for%20this%20confusion.%20From%20there%20to%20politicisation%20was%20a%20short%20distance.%20After%20all%2C%20when%20religion%2C%20nation%20and%20party%20are%20one%2C%20how%20can%20one%20distinguish!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIs%20there%20a%20way%20to%20climb%20out%20of%20this%20morass%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20Rajouri-Poonch%20incident%20has%20offered%20a%20chance%20to%20start%20the%20process%20of%20recovery.%20Distinguish%20between%20criminality%20and%20a%20genuine%20mistake.%20Instead%20of%20incentivising%20criminal%20behaviour%20using%20the%20plea%20of%20troops%E2%80%99%20morale%2C%20prosecute%20and%20punish%20the%20criminals%20in%20uniform.%20Make%20an%20example%20of%20them.%20Sure%2C%20this%20will%20only%20be%20a%20patchwork.%20But%20until%20the%20military%20finds%20the%20muscle%20to%20stand%20up%20and%20tell%20the%20political%20leadership%20that%20it%20needs%20to%20go%20back%20to%20the%20barracks%20to%20resurrect%20its%20core%20values%2C%20patchwork%20will%20have%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EGhazala%20Wahab%20is%20editor%20%3C%2Fem%3EFORCE%3Cem%3E%20magazine.%20Her%20books%20include%20%3C%2Fem%3EDragon%20On%20Our%20Doorstep%3A%20Managing%20China%20Through%20Military%20Power%2C%20Born%20A%20Muslim%3A%20Some%20Truths%20About%20Islam%20in%20India%3Cem%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Peacemakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704072614000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F31172500%2FGAqdk2CWAAA3rZ-.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fhow-the-quicksand-of-counter-insurgency-operations-has-hurt-indian-armys-core-value%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20rec