2%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222237%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22fuzzy%20dice%20mirror%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6591f17aab6f2ebb11f7fc7c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221678%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20pair%20of%20fuzzy%20dice%20hang%20on%20a%20rear-view%20mirror.%3Cp%3ERusty%20Jarrett%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20NASCAR%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20hundreds%20of%20new%20laws%20are%20set%20to%20take%20effect.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOne%20of%20them%20includes%20an%20Illinois%20law%20that%20will%20make%20rearview%20mirror%20decor%20legal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20minimum%20wage%20will%20also%20increase%20in%20several%20states.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFuzzy%20dice%20will%20finally%20be%20free%20to%20dangle%20in%20Illinois.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStarting%20Monday%2C%20police%20in%20the%20state%20will%20no%20longer%20be%20allowed%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ilga.gov%2Flegislation%2Fpublicacts%2Ffulltext.asp%3FName%3D103-0032%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epull%20over%20motorists%3C%2Fa%3E%20solely%20because%20they%20have%20something%20hanging%20from%20their%20windshield's%20rearview%20mirror.%20That%20means%20air%20fresheners%2C%20parking%20placards%2C%20and%2C%20yes%2C%20even%20those%20dice%20are%20fair%20game%20to%20hang.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20revised%20Illinois%20windshield%20rule%20is%20one%20of%20hundreds%20of%20new%20laws%20taking%20effect%20with%20the%20new%20year%20in%20states%20across%20the%20US.%20While%20some%20may%20seem%20a%20bit%20pedestrian%2C%20others%20have%20practical%20impacts%20or%20touch%20on%20controversial%20issues%2C%20such%20as%20restrictions%20on%20weapons%20and%20medical%20treatments%20for%20transgender%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20original%20Illinois%20windshield%20law%20was%20meant%20to%20improve%20roadway%20safety%2C%20it%20came%20to%20be%20seen%20by%20some%20as%20an%20excuse%20for%20pulling%20over%20drivers.%20The%20new%20law%20still%20prohibits%20objects%20that%20obstruct%20a%20driver's%20view%20but%20forbids%20law%20enforcement%20officers%20from%20conducting%20stops%20or%20searches%20solely%20because%20of%20suspected%20violations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20this%20new%20law%2C%20we%20are%20sending%20a%20powerful%20message%20that%20the%20state%20does%20not%20tolerate%20racial%20profiling%20or%20other%20forms%20of%20discrimination%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Democratic%20state%20Sen.%20Christopher%20Belt%2C%20one%20of%20the%20bill's%20sponsors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20new%20Illinois%20law%20seeks%20to%20stifle%20a%20more%20modern%20form%20of%20distracted%20driving%20by%20prohibiting%20people%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ilga.gov%2Flegislation%2Ffulltext.asp%3FDocName%3D%26SessionId%3D112%26GA%3D103%26DocTypeId%3DHB%26DocNum%3D2431%26GAID%3D17%26LegID%3D147512%26SpecSess%3D%26Session%3D%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eparticipating%20in%20video%20conferences%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20scanning%20social%20media%20while%20behind%20the%20wheel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EGuns%20will%20be%20regulated%20after%20a%20record%20year%20of%20shootings%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20states%20have%20new%20laws%20regulating%20guns%20and%20online%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Minnesota%20law%20will%20allow%20authorities%20to%20ask%20courts%20for%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fgun-control-safety-minnesota-governor-f7f7d0276061b01890b623b535780fd6%3Futm_source%3Dcopy%26utm_medium%3Dshare%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eextreme%20risk%20protection%20orders%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20to%20temporarily%20take%20guns%20from%20people%20deemed%20to%20be%20an%20imminent%20threat%20to%20others%20or%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMinnesota%20will%20be%20at%20least%20the%2020th%20state%20with%20such%20a%20red-flag%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EColorado%20will%20become%20one%20of%20a%20dozen%20states%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2F