%20your%20devices%20and%20can't%20recall%20which%20password%20is%20associated%20with%20your%20Apple%20ID%2C%20then%20you%20have%20a%20slightly%20larger%20problem%2C%20but%20there%20is%20a%20solution%3A%20use%20Apple's%20iForgot%20site%20to%20reset%20your%20Apple%20ID%20password%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGo%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fiforgot.apple.com%2Fpassword%2Fverify%2Fappleid%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eiforgot.apple.com%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Ideally%2C%20you%20will%20be%20doing%20this%20on%20a%20Mac%20associated%20with%20your%20account.%20If%20you%20can't%20do%20that%2C%20make%20sure%20an%20iPhone%20associated%20with%20your%20account%20is%20on%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20iForgot%20site%2C%20enter%20the%20mobile%20phone%20number%20associated%20with%20your%20Apple%20account%20along%20with%20the%20captcha%20displayed%20on%20the%20screen.%20Then%20click%20%26quot%3BContinue%26quot%3B%20and%20follow%20the%20prompt%20on%20the%20next%20page%20to%20enter%20your%20Apple%20ID%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20click%20%26quot%3BContinue%2C%26quot%3B%20prompts%20will%20automatically%20be%20sent%20to%20your%20phone%20and%20computer%20asking%20if%20it's%20OK%20to%20use%20one%20of%20those%20devices%20to%20reset%20your%20password.%20Click%20or%20tap%20to%20give%20permission%2C%20then%20follow%20the%20prompts%20to%20reset%20your%20Apple%20ID%20password%2C%20which%20will%20end%2C%20for%20now%2C%20with%20you%20waiting%20for%20an%20account%20recovery%20email%20from%20Apple.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20do%20I%20check%20my%20iForgot%20Apple%20status%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESubmitting%20a%20password%20change%20request%20via%20Apple's%20iForgot%20site%20isn't%20all%20that%20complicated%2C%20but%20it's%20also%20not%20quite%20as%20rapid-fire%20as%20you%20may%20be%20used%20to%20in%20our%20digital%20world.%20In%20fact%2C%20per%20Apple%2C%20it%20may%20take%20up%20to%2072%20hours%20for%20your%20account%20recovery%20email%20to%20be%20sent%20after%2