s%E2%80%9D%20to%20celebrate%20Diwali%20on%20January%2022%2C%202024%2C%20the%20day%20when%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20temple%20will%20be%20inaugurated%20by%20him.%20He%20asked%20everyone%20to%20light%20a%20lamp%20in%20their%20houses%2C%20and%20urged%20all%20not%20to%20crowd%20Ayodhya%20on%20the%20day%20of%20inauguration.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20have%20waited%20for%20more%20than%20500%20years.%20Do%20wait%20for%20some%20more%20days%20and%20then%20come%20to%20Ayodhya%20after%20considering%20all%20the%20security%20aspects%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20prime%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLight%20a%20Ram%20jyoti%20in%20your%20respective%20houses%20when%20the%20Lord%20reaches%20his%20new%20home%3B%20celebrate%20Diwali%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20even%20as%20he%20and%20all%20the%20other%20BJP%20leaders%20missed%20no%20opportunity%20to%20convey%20that%20Lord%20Ram%20will%20be%20returning%20to%20his%20home%20after%20a%20gap%20of%20500%20years%20%E2%80%93%20a%20political%20instrument%20to%20remind%20people%20that%20the%20supposedly%20original%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20temple%20was%20destroyed%20by%20the%20%E2%80%9CMughal%20invaders%E2%80%9D%20to%20build%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20at%20its%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20went%20on%20to%20add%2C%20while%20talking%20about%20India%E2%80%99s%20long%20strides%20in%20digital%20technology%20even%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20preserving%20pilgrimage%20sites%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20the%20same%20Ayodhya%20where%20Ram%20Lalla%20lived%20in%20a%20tent%20for%20years.%20But%20now%20not%20only%20has%20Ram%20got%20a%20permanent%20temple%2C%20but%20also%20four%20crore%20people%20have%20received%20their%20own%20permanent%20house%20(under%20PM%20Awas%20Yojana).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESocial%20media%20was%20also%20flooded%20with%20videos%20of%20how%20people%20were%20celebrating%20the%20new%20Ram%20temple%20and%20modern%20infrastructure%20in%20Ayodhya%20alike.%20The%20passengers%20of%20the%20first%20Indigo%20flight%20to%20Ayodhya%20were%20seen%20chanting%20Ram%20Bhajans%20in%20the%20cabin%2C%20even%20as%20the%20Captain%20addressed%20them%20as%20being%20the%20fortunate%20one%20to%20pilot%20the%20first%20flight%20to%20Ayodhya%2C%20ending%20his%20speech%20with%20%E2%80%9CJai%20Siya%20Ram%E2%80%9D.%20Supporters%20of%20Hindutva%20organised%20themselves%20to%20lash%20out%20at%20%E2%80%9CLeft%2C%20liberals%2C%20English-speaking%20seculars%E2%80%9D%20for%20%E2%80%9Cderacinating%E2%80%9D%20Indians%20through%20their%20deliberate%20erasure%20of%20Hindu%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%20we%20are%20witnessing%20the%20grandeur%20of%20development%2C%20and%20after%20a%20few%20days%20we%20will%20see%20the%20splendour%20of%20heritage.%20%3Cem%3EYahi%20toh%20Bharat%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%20(This%20is%20all%20India%20is%20all%20about)%2C%E2%80%9D%20Modi%20declared%2C%20fusing%20his%20messages%20of%20vikas%20and%20virasat.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704022073000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F31154445%2FGCmRH66WEAAejGQ.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fweeks-before-ram-temple-inauguration-pm-modi-and-a-pr-blitzkrieg-visit-ayodhya%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22All%20three%20pillars%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20politics%20%E2%80%93%20Hindutva%2C%20development%20and%20welfare%20%E2%80%93%20were%20covered%20in%20Modi's%20speeches%20and%20agenda.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fweeks-before-ram-temple-inauguration-pm-modi-and-a-pr-blitzkrieg-visit-ayodhya%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Auto%20sales%20surge%2011%25%20in%202023%2C%20marginally%20short%20of%20pre-Covid%20numbers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704021711000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2019-08%2F28%2Ffull%2F1567010510-8064.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22http