very%20sick.%20He%20put%20his%20head%20down%20the%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20much%20time%20had%20passed%20when%20he%20became%20conscious%20again%20and%20attempted%20to%20rise%20from%20his%20chair.%20He%20faltered%20and%20had%20the%20sensation%20of%20something%20cold%20and%20very%20hard%20hitting%20him%20on%20his%20forehead.%20Rahman%20miyan%20crashed%20to%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20the%20evening%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESalman%20was%20never%20sweet%20to%20his%20mother.%20She%20had%20lived%20and%20worked%20all%20her%20life%20in%20the%20house%20of%20an%20old%2C%20illustrious%20family.%20Salman%2C%20who%20had%20never%20known%20his%20father%2C%20had%20grown%20up%20angry%20in%20the%20servants%E2%80%99%20quarters%20behind%20the%20main%20kothi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20found%20his%20mother%20in%20the%20kitchen%20courtyard%20supervising%20her%20new%20helper%20while%20he%20cleaned%20the%20mutton%20for%20the%20day%E2%80%99s%20dinner%20in%20the%20kothi.%20Zaitoon%20nani%2C%20the%20oldest%20member%20of%20the%20staff%2C%20was%20also%20there%2C%20resting%20on%20her%20small%20chowki.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAmma!%20What%E2%80%99s%20for%20dinner%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20only%20six.%20You%20want%20dinner%20now!%20I%20have%20to%20first%20cook%20dinner%20for%20the%20table.%20Why%20do%20you%20want%20dinner%20now%3F%20You%20haven%E2%80%99t%20even%20been%20out%20on%20your%20evening%20jaunt%20yet.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20way%20he%20was%20dressed%2C%20in%20tight%2C%20tapered%20pants%20and%20an%20equally%20tight-fitting%20jacket%2C%20it%20was%20obvious%20that%20he%20was%20intending%20to%20go%20out%20and%20didn%E2%80%99t%20really%20want%20dinner.%20Salman%20scowled%20at%20her%20and%20turned%20to%20leave.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ll%20eat%20out%20then.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThen%20why%20were%20you%20asking%20me%3F%20Anyway%20you%20eat%20out%20%E2%80%93%20sometimes%20at%20Laadley%E2%80%99s%2C%20sometimes%20at%20that%20witch%20Naseeban%E2%80%99s%20house.%20How%20she%20has%20done%20black%20magic%20on%20you!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZaitoon%20nani%20clucked%20her%20tongue.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20is%20a%20very%20bad%20influence%2C%20Sallu.%20You%20are%20wasting%20your%20time%20instead%20of%20finding%20work.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFinding%20work%3F%E2%80%9D%20Salman%20scoffed.%20%E2%80%9CNani%2C%20why%20don%E2%80%99t%20you%20ask%20Badey%20saheb%20to%20get%20me%20some%20decent%20work%3F%20I%20promise%20I%E2%80%99ll%20leave%20everything%20and%20focus.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHow%20will%20he%20find%20you%20work%3F%E2%80%9D%20said%20his%20mother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20is%20a%20big%20man.%20He%20knows%20everybody.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20it%20is%3A%20in%20our%20community%2C%20important%20people%20turn%20their%20faces%20away%20from%20people%20like%20me.%20They%20don%E2%80%99t%20meet%20our%20eyes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20embarrassment%2C%20They%20can%E2%80%99t%20help%2C%20so%20then%20what%20is%20the%20point%20of%20looking%3F%E2%80%9D%20At%20times%20Zaitoon%20nani%20could%20be%20very%20perceptive%20about%20her%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLook%20at%20Bulbhaddar%20babu%3A%20he%20has%20helped%20Shambhu%20and%20those%20two%20thugs%2C%20Kanwal%20and%20Nirmal.%20There%20is%20nobody%20to%20help%20us.%20Amma%2C%20why%20didn%E2%80%99t%20you%20at%20least%20send%20me%20to%20a%20proper%20school%3F%20She%20sent%20me%20to%20a%20madarsa%20to%20save%20money.%20Now%20I%20am%20stuck.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20have%20a%2010th%C2%A0class%20certificate.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20work%20night%20and%20day%20to%20feed%20you.%20Where%20was%20the%20money%20to%20send%20you%20to%20an%20English%20school%3F%E2%80%9D%20said%20his%20mother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBeta%2C%20even%20if%20you%20had%20gone%20to%20the%20most%20famous%20English%20school%2C%20you%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20had%20any%20papers%20to%20show.%20You%20get%20a%20degree%20if%20you%20properly%20pass%20your%20exams.%20When%20you%20keep%20running%20away%20from%20school%2C%20then%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20matter%20whether%20it%20is%20an%20English%20school%20or%20an%20Arabi%20school%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Zaitoon%20nani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESalman%20shrugged%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20have%20a%20birth%20certificate%2C%20or%20any%20other%20certificate.%20When%20they%20come%20with%20the%20NRC%20register%2C%20what%20will%20I%20do%3F%20Fine!%20Let%20them%20put%20my%20name%20on%20the%20register%20and%20deport%20me.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20care.%20My%20Amma%20and%20my%20nani%20will%20have%20each%20other.%E2%80%9D%20He%20banged%20the%20wooden%20courtyard%20door%20as%20he%20left.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20does%20he%20suddenly%20want%20papers%3F%E2%80%9D%20his%20mother%20asked%2C%20looking%20towards%20Zaitoon%20nani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CArshad%20bhai%2C%20please%20take%20me%20in%3F%20Put%20me%20with%20Abrar%20bhai%20%E2%80%93%20I%20will%20peel%20onions%3B%20I%20will%20clean%20the%20gosht%3B%20I%20will%20do%20everything%2C%E2%80%9D%20Salman%20begged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20late%20and%20most%20customers%20had%20left.%20Abrar%2C%20the%20cook%2C%20was%20sitting%20on%20his%20haunches%20and%20smoking%20a%20beedi.%20%E2%80%9CHave%20you%20ever%20peeled%20onions%20in%20your%20life%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20snapped%20at%20Salman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThen%20let%20me%20train%20under%20you%2C%20Arshad%20bhai%2C%20please%3F%20You%20are%20overworked.%20You%20need%20a%20helper%2C%E2%80%9D%20Salman%20pleaded%20with%20Arshad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArshad%20considered%20this%20line%20of%20argument%20and%20nodded%20to%20himself.%20%E2%80%9CSalman%2C%20but%20you%20will%20have%20to%20listen%20and%20take%20orders%20from%20me.%20You%20don%E2%80%99t%20listen%20to%20anybody%3B%20that%20is%20your%20problem.%20Come%20let%E2%80%99s%20ask%20haji%20saheb%20if%20we%20can%20keep%20you.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahman%20miyan%20was%20busy%20tallying%20accounts%20at%20the%20end%20of%20a%20busy%20day%2C%20and%20coughing%20alongside.%20He%20looked%20up%20as%20Salman%20hesitatingly%20followed%20Arshad%20inside%20the%20restaurant%2C%20and%20made%20a%20face%20of%20disgust%20and%20disapproval.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20he%20doing%20here%3F%20Who%20allowed%20him%20in%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHaji%20saheb%2C%20he%20has%20reformed%20now.%20He%20wants%20a%20job%2C%20and%20I%20thought%20we%20might%20employ%20him%20as%20my%20helper.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYour%20helper%3F%20You%20are%20already%20my%20helper%2C%20and%20now%20you%20want%20you%20own%20helper%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArshad%20remained%20silent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20wait%20outside%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rahman%20miyan%20said%20to%20Salman.%20He%20then%20turned%20to%20Arshad%20and%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20doing%20my%20accounts.%20The%20almirah%20is%20open%3B%20the%20cash%20box%20is%20in%20full%20view.%20You%20should%20know%20better%20than%20bringing%20him%20here.%20Anyway%2C%20I%20have%20decided%20to%20pass%20on%20the%20restaurant%20to%20my%20begum%E2%80%99s%20nephew.%20In%20fact%2C%20she%20has%20gone%20to%20her%20brother%E2%80%99s%20house%20to%20discuss%20the%20plan%20with%20them.%20Now%20let%20the%20boy%20first%20join%20the%20team.%20He%20might%20want%20to%20modernise%20everything%2C%20and%20bring%20English-speaking%20waiters.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20serve%20paaya%3F%E2%80%9D%20Arshad%20asked%20incredulously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESalman%20had%20been%20standing%20by%20the%20door%2C%20looking%20forlorn.%20Just%20then%20a%20motorcycle%20screeched%20to%20a%20halt.%20The%20pillion%20rider%20jumped%20off%20first%20and%20waited%20for%20the%20driver%20to%20alight%20and%20take%20his%20helmet%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COho%2C%20world-famous%20loafer%20Salman%20ji%20himself%20at%20your%20doorstep%20to%20welcome%20customers%2C%20Rahman%20ji%3F%E2%80%9D%20Constable%20Awdhesh%20Rana%20called%20out%20to%20Rahman%20miyan%20as%20he%20strode%20into%20the%20restaurant.%20Kanwal%2C%20the%20pillion%20rider%2C%20walked%20in%20behind%20him%2C%20smirking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20saying%20to%20Kanwal%20ji%20that%20I%20will%20take%20you%20for%20some%20good%20quality%20meat-mutton%20tonight%2C%20but%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20I%20should%20even%20be%20seen%20at%20your%20restaurant%20anymore.%20Imagine%20a%20policeman%20and%20his%20guest%20eating%20at%20the%20same%20place%20as%20a%20local%20rowdy!%20Kyun%20bhai%2C%20Salman%20Romeo%2C%20you%20have%20also%20come%20to%20eat%3F%E2%80%9D%20He%20turned%20to%20look%20at%20Salman%20who%20was%20still%20standing%20at%20the%20threshold.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahman%20miyan%20half%20rose%20in%20his%20chair%20in%20welcome%20and%20in%20panic%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20myself%20thrown%20him%20out%20just%20as%20you%20arrived%20Inspector%20saheb.%20Get%20out!%E2%80%9D%20he%20shouted%20in%20a%20rather%20undignified%20manner%20at%20Salman%2C%20and%20burst%20into%20another%20coughing%20fit.%20%E2%80%9CWhere%E2%80%99s%20Abrar%3F%20Tell%20him%20to%20light%20the%20ovens%20%E2%80%93%20make%20fresh%20rotis.%20Sit%2C%20sit%20Inspector%20saheb%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20gestured%20with%20both%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConstable%20Awdhesh%20Rana%20belched%20loudly.%20Rahman%20miyan%2C%20who%20was%20watching%20anxiously%20asked%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20food%20suits%20you%2C%20Inspector%20saheb%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConstable%20Rana%20looked%20at%20his%20plate%20thoughtfully%20and%20said%20without%20malice%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20roti%20could%20have%20been%20a%20little%20more%20crisp%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20Rahman%20miyan%20turned%20towards%20the%20kitchen%20and%20shouted%20in%20his%20deep%20voice%2C%20%E2%80%9CAbrar!%20Did%20you%20hear%20that%3F%20You%E2%80%99re%20serving%20uncooked%20roti%20to%20Inspector%20sahib%20no