20the%20floor%2C%20face%20down%2C%20his%20forehead%20had%20a%20deep%20gash%20and%20was%20pressed%20against%20the%20steam%20iron%2C%20which%20was%20also%20lying%20on%20the%20floor.%20Haji%20saheb%20had%20turned%20black.%20There%20was%20so%20much%20blood%2C%E2%80%9D%20Arshad%20shivered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSomebody%20has%20stolen%20the%20gosht%20ka%20pateela%20from%20the%20kitchen%2C%20with%20all%20the%20paaya%20in%20it.%20Other%20pateelas%20are%20also%20missing.%20Haji%20saheb%E2%80%99s%20aluminium%20tiffin%20carrier%20is%20gone%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Abrar%20quietly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20robbery%20inside%20also.%20His%20counter%20has%20been%20toppled%20over%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Arshad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaadley%20put%20his%20hands%20on%20Arshad%E2%80%99s%20shoulders%2C%20ostensibly%20in%20order%20to%20comfort%20him%2C%20but%20it%20only%20made%20Arshad%20lose%20his%20balance%20and%20stumble%20slightly.%20%E2%80%9CArre%2C%20he%20will%20faint%20from%20the%20sadma%2C%E2%80%9D%20shouted%20Salman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20be%20melodramatic%2C%E2%80%9D%20Abrar%20snapped%20back.%20At%20that%20moment%2C%20Arshad%20and%20Abrar%20were%20both%20summoned%20inside%20by%20begum%20saheba%20to%20receive%20instructions%20regarding%20the%20funeral.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20there%20last%20night%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Jamal%20glancing%20towards%20Habib.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20a%20long%20conversation%20with%20him%2C%20no%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20after%20everyone%20left%2C%20Awdhesh%20Rana%20and%20Kanwal%20came%20to%20the%20restaurant%20and%20even%20threatened%20haji%20saheb.%20I%20was%20there%20in%20the%20beginning%2C%20but%20they%20made%20me%20leave%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Salman%20conspiratorially.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CKanwal%20was%20there%20too%3F%20What%20was%20that%20scoundrel%20doing%20in%20our%20gali%3F%E2%80%9D%20Laadley%20spat%20on%20the%20ground.%20%E2%80%9CNow%20we%20know%20who%20is%20responsible%20for%20this.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJamal%E2%80%99s%20father%2C%20Asghar%2C%20returned%20with%20Balabhadra%20babu%20to%20Rahman%20miyan%E2%80%99s%20house%2C%20where%20the%20whole%20mohalla%20was%20gathered.%20Both%20declared%20that%20they%20had%20%E2%80%98spoken%20to%20people%E2%80%99%20and%20that%20the%20body%20would%20be%20returned%20by%20Asr%20time%20for%20burial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20spoken%20to%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20Balabhadra%20babu%20said%20confidently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20requested%20Achche%20to%20intervene%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Asghar%20supportively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20also%20tried%20helpfully%20to%20answer%20people%E2%80%99s%20questions%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNo%2C%20no%20Beta%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20if%20his%20head%20was%20smashed%20with%20the%20steam%20iron%20or%20whether%20he%20fell%20on%20top%20of%20it.%20Post%20mortem%20results%20are%20awaited%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Balabhadra%20babu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20injury%20to%20the%20head%20could%20be%20ante-mortem.%20The%20concerned%20person%20said%20that%20the%20body%20was%20blue%20and%20it%20seemed%20he%20had%20choked%20on%20something%20%E2%80%93%20it%20could%20be%20an%20asthma%20attack%20even%2C%E2%80%9D%20Asghar%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20mean%20it%20isn%E2%80%99t%20a%20murder%3F%20But%20there%20has%20been%20a%20robbery%20too.%20Abrar%20is%20saying%20that%20the%20gosht%20ka%20pateela%20is%20gone%2C%E2%80%9D%20asked%20Habib.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThen%20it%20has%20to%20be%20a%20Mohammadan%20who%20has%20done%20it!%20We%20won%E2%80%99t%20kill%20for%20gosht%20ka%20pateela%2C%E2%80%9D%20blurted%20Shambhu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBalabhadra%20babu%20gave%20him%20an%20annoyed%20look%2C%20and%20then%20changed%20the%20subject.%20%E2%80%9CArre%20Abrar%2C%20why%20don%E2%80%99t%20you%20serve%20some%20biscuits%3F%20Body%20will%20still%20take%20some%20hours.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20afternoon%2C%20the%20men%20of%20the%20mohalla%20waited%20for%20the%20body%20to%20arrive%2C%20while%20Abrar%20went%20around%20serving%20Parle-G%20biscuits%2C%20arranged%20on%20a%20stainless%20steel%20tray.%20Rahman%20miyan%E2%80%99s%20nephews%20went%20to%20arrange%20a%20place%20at%20the%20local%20cemetery.%20Later%2C%20Laadley%20and%20Arshad%20were%20dispatched%20to%20oversee%20the%20digging%20of%20the%20grave%3B%20the%20children%20continued%20to%20read%20the%20Quran%20on%20empty%20stomachs%3B%20begum%20saheba%20continued%20to%20wail%3B%20the%20young%20moulvi%20from%20the%20madarsa%20made%20preparations%20to%20give%20a%20ritual%20ghusl%20to%20Rahman%20miyan%E2%80%99s%20body%3B%20and%20Asghar%20and%20Balabhadra%20babu%20went%20back%20to%20the%20hospital%20to%20receive%20the%20body.%20Of%20course%20Rahmania%20hotel%20remained%20closed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20men%20finally%20returned%20from%20the%20Qabristan%2C%20it%20was%20cold%20and%20dark.%20Laadley%20had%20had%20some%20lights%20and%20some%20plastic%20chairs%20put%20outside%20Rahman%20miyan%E2%80%99s%20house.%20The%20man%20in%20the%20sleeveless%20brown%20sweater%20and%20checked%20lungi%20served%20tea%20and%20more%20Parle-G%20biscuits.%20Jamal%E2%80%99s%20mother%20sent%20some%20cooked%20food%20for%20Begum%20saheba%20and%20her%20immediate%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20day%20drew%20to%20a%20close%2C%20Constable%20Rana%20who%20had%20earlier%20come%20to%20seal%20the%20restaurant%20rode%20up%20to%20the%20house%20and%20and%20parked%20in%20a%20dark%20corner.%20He%20didn%E2%80%99t%20get%20off%20from%20his%20bike%2C%20but%20nodded%20at%20Arshad%20and%20signalled%20for%20him%20to%20come%20over.%20%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20mention%20to%20anybody%20that%20I%20was%20there%20last%20night.%20It%20was%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20confidential%20and%20sensitive%20investigation.%20If%20word%20leaks%20out%2C%20I%E2%80%99ll%20find%20you.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EShahrukh%20Alam%20has%20be