s%20and%20Some%20Subversive%20Turns%3A%20The%20Best%20Hindi%20Films%20of%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20different%20kind%20of%20courage%20is%20the%20moral%20core%20of%20another%20miniseries%20%3Cem%3ETrial%20by%20Fire%20%3C%2Fem%3Eabout%20another%20tragedy%20in%201997%2C%20in%20which%20a%20fire%20accident%20in%20a%20cinema%20hall%20Uphaar%20Cinema%20in%20South%20Delhi%20led%20to%20the%20death%20of%2059%20people%20and%20serious%20injuries%20to%20103%20others.%20The%20story%20is%20recounted%20here%20through%20the%20staggeringly%20dogged%20unwavering%20struggle%20stretched%20over%20two%20decades%20of%20Neelam%20Krishnamoorthy%20and%20her%20husband%20Shekhar%2C%20who%20had%20lost%20both%20their%20children%20in%20the%20fire%20accident.%20Their%20profound%20loss%20and%20sorrow%20drives%20Neelam%2C%20supported%20steadfastly%20by%20her%20husband%2C%20to%20relentlessly%2C%20even%20obsessively%20pursue%20justice%20from%20the%20courts.%20The%20criminal%20cases%20against%20the%20cinema%20owners%2C%20the%20Ansal%20brothers%2C%20who%20had%20violated%20elementary%20safety%20norms%2C%20and%20the%20managers%20of%20the%20theatre%20move%20at%20a%20glacial%20pace%20through%20the%20Kafkaesque%20maze%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20judicial%20system.%20In%20the%20end%20the%20courts%20let%20off%20those%20criminally%20guilty%20of%20causing%20so%20many%20deaths%20all%20too%20lightly.%20Justice%20fails%20Neelam%20and%20Shekhar%2C%20but%20they%20are%20victorious%20in%20the%20ways%20they%20uphold%20the%20tenacity%20of%20the%20human%20spirit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F31115205%2FTrial-By-Fire.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F31