song%20and%20two%20years%20later%20composed%20and%20recorded%20his%20first%20song%20%E2%80%98Listen%20to%20Your%20Heart%E2%80%99%20on%20a%20mobile%20phone%20at%20his%20grandmother%E2%80%99s%20place.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20first%20song%20I%20recorded%20was%20on%20a%20phone.%20I%20transferred%20the%20audio%20to%20a%20computer%20and%20used%20a%20software%20called%20Virtual%20DJ%20where%20I%20had%20to%20sync%20the%20music%20and%20audio%20without%20any%20mixing%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20reminisces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20writing%20songs%20and%20making%20music%2C%20Moko%20was%20also%20a%20good%20student.%20After%20high%20school%2C%20he%20got%20into%20the%20prestigious%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F259970%2Fmiracradle-niranjan-thomas-india-asphyxia-newborns-treatment-low-cost-innovation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChristian%20Medical%20College%20(CMC)%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20Vellore%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20to%20study%20medicine%20but%20turned%20down%20the%20opportunity%20to%20study%20there.%20He%20makes%20a%20reference%20to%20this%20event%20in%20the%20first%20verse%20of%20his%20latest%20single%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EAji%20Kali%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20which%20was%20released%20earlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-epautoplay%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20data-facadesrc%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FbylHAbo9yw8%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26amp%3Bautoplay%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_load_policy%3D0%26amp%3Biv_load_policy%3D3%26amp%3Bloop%3D0%26amp%3Bmodestbranding%3D0%26amp%3Bfs%3D1%26amp%3Bplaysinline%3D1%26amp%3Bcontrols%3D1%26amp%3Bcolor%3Dred%26amp%3Bcc_lang_pref%3D%26amp%3Brel%3D0%26amp%3Bautohide%3D2%26amp%3Btheme%3Ddark%26amp%3B%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%