3EBefore%20releasing%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3ENaga%20Manu%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20in%20August%202022%2C%20Moko%20Koza%20caught%20the%20ears%20of%20Hip%20Hop%20aficionados%20from%20around%20the%20country%20with%20his%20battle%20rap%20songs%20and%20cyphers%20marked%20by%20interesting%20wordplay%2C%20flow%20and%20cadence.%20But%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3ENaga%20Manu%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20really%20put%20him%20on%20the%20map.%20The%20inspiration%20came%20from%20his%20memory%20of%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EPuisa%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20first%20Nagamese%20song%20he%20put%20out%2C%20and%20the%20good%20reception%20it%20got%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EPuisa%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20means%20money%20in%20Nagamese%2C%20reflects%20on%20how%20the%20youth%20are%20exhausted%20by%20systemic%20corruption%20that%20has%20afflicted%20Nagaland%20for%20decades.%20Nagamese%20is%20the%20commonly%20accepted%20lingua%20franca%20in%20a%20state%20with%20many%20tribes%20that%20have%20their%20own%20indigenous%20languages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20the%20response%20to%20%3Cem%3EPuisa%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewas%20good%2C%20I%20thought%20about%20making%20more%20Nagamese%20songs.%20Writing%20and%20rapping%20in%20Nagamese%20and%20other%20dialects%20has%20introduced%20me%20to%20a%20whole%20new%20audience%2C%20particularly%20the%20older%20generations.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3ENaga%20Manu%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20I%20recognised%20that%20not%20everyone%20has%20the%20voice%20to%20speak%20for%20the%20community.%20As%20an%20artist%2C%20I%20have%20that%20platform.%20So%2C%20I%20really%20wanted%20to%20address%20some%20key%20social%20issues%20in%20Nagaland%20like%20alcohol%20prohibition%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Moko.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20if%20we%20talk%20about%20something%20very%20serious%2C%20people%20don%E2%80%99t%20usually%20listen.%20So%20I%20thought%20of%20bringing%20in%20some%20humour%20so%20that%20people%20would%20listen.%20This%20helped%20me%20establish%20the%2